{"code":200,"msg":"success","data":[{"id":238,"createTime":"2019-06-03 10:23:23","topicId":null,"tagId":46,"rule":4,"weight":1,"sort":1,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p style=\"line-height:24px;background:white\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:宋体\">关节痛</span></strong></p><table><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(227, 108, 9);\"><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、病因诱因：是否受凉、劳累、妊娠、分娩、感染、精神紧张。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、主要症状特点：起病急缓？病程（演变？）性质（是否游走性？有无红肿热痛、关节畸形？）程度？和天气、活动的关系？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、伴随症状：有无发热、皮疹、肌肉疼痛、肌无力、肌萎缩、淋巴肿大、肝脾肿大？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、全身状态：发病以来饮食、睡眠、大小便及体重变化</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、诊疗经过：发病以来是否到医院检查过，曾做过哪些检查和治疗（x片、风湿系列、血沉）？非甾类解热镇痛药、激素、抗生素治疗情况？治疗是否有效？</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">、相关病史：(1)有无药物过敏史、手术史</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 24px; background: white; border: none; padding: 1px 5px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">(2)</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">既往有无类似发作史？有无关节病史、关节外伤史、结核史、风湿史、疑有传染病时还应注意流行病史？</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br/></p>","trueCnt":0,"falseCnt":0,"analysis":"","topic":null,"options":[],"tags":[{"id":46,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-01 13:45:21","updateTime":"2019-06-01 13:45:21","name":"⑤关节痛","questionCnt":1,"tagTypeId":15},{"id":285,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-01 16:03:24","updateTime":"2019-06-01 16:03:24","name":"关节痛","questionCnt":1,"tagTypeId":19}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null}]}